text: Bitch! Tere paas super power hai, tere saath sirf maza aata hai sabko (usually jiski tu gaand maar rha hai uske expense pe lol). Meri campus ki best memories mein tu hai. Bohot chill kiya apan ne aur karte rahenge.
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text:
Never have I seen a person excel at everything and make it seem effortless. Endsem mein meri gaand phati hoti this and you used to glide around in the wing, chill as fuck. In life, if I feel overwhelmed by a challenge, I will think of you and try to embody a bit of that Bhatia coolness. Tune starting mein jo parties miss ki unke liye makeup kar liye end mein, lol. Mai bohot lucky feel karta hu ki apan itne achhe dost bane. Bohot maze kiye, aur karte rahenge! 
Bakchod Bhatia!
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: Our leader chandu! Pehli baar tere saath high hua thha mai! Bohot mast memory hai, uske baad toh apan ne bohot saari aur bana li!
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: Chillest dude ever! Bohot mast moments enjoy kiye apan ne. Dankness ka living embodiment hai tu. JItne meme pages follow karta hu sab tune recommend kiye hai. Vibe creator hai tu. Apan milte rahenge!!
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: Lil' dikky! Harami log bhi achhe hote hai tujhse seekha hu mai. Iss last year mein tu nahi rahega bohot ajeeb lagega. But hum log aa hi rhe hai next year, tab bhi maza ayega.  Tu nahi hota toh subnautica kabhi khatam nahi kar pata, toh thanks. Milte rahenge, awkward nahi hoga pakka lol.
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: Iss last sem campus aaye saath mein aur fir roz chill kiya apan ne. Bohot maza aaya bohot saari daaru peeke, lol. Aage bhi milte rahenge ab toh!
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: You came from the shadows, and into our hearts,lol. When you become famous, I'm going to sell all the stuff you made on madhur's ipad.
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: Ghisuu! Tu hi reason hai ki mujhe mera phone locked rakhna padta hai. I feel lucky ki hum itne achhe dost bane. Tu mujhe khush dekh hi nahi paata thha aur ungli karne aa jaata thha lol. But woh meri campus ki some of the best memories ban gayi. Tu chaapega aage bhi jaise tune campus mein chaapa hai. Milte rahenge apan.
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: Kevlin you are the nicest and kindest person on campus and one of my best friends ever.  Yugesh aap aur mai first year mein hi family jaise ban gaye. Aapki energetic aur positive presence sabko khush kar deti hai. Bohot lucky hu mai ki hum roomies the aur fir itne achhe dost ban gaye. Aage milte rahenge!
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: MDJ! The supreme dominator! Life of the party! Kuch zyada hi maze kar liye apan ne campus mein lol. Apni gang waalo se ekdum family waali feeling aati hai. Tu kaunsa family member hoga guess kar,lol.
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: Campus mein sabse zyada tere saath chill kiya hai, aage bhi karte rahenge definitely. Itni saari memories hai ki mai sort bhi nahi kar paunga dimaag mein. Kaafi saari bohot nashe mein bhi thhi to be honest lol. Bohot maze kiye, next trip mein tu chalega pakka.
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: Roomies for life! 4 saal almost har test ke liye saath mein pdhayi ki hai. Agar hum ek dusre ki attendance nahi lagate toh dono graduate nahi ho pate, lol! Bohot maze kiye, aage bhi karte rahenge!
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: Bitch! The golden boy of G-Bot. Apan toh milte rahenge! Bohot adventures baaki hai abhi toh. There are literally very few campus memories without you. We had the best times together but there is a lot more to come. See you soon. Apne plans mat bhoolna, ps5 aur tv pehli salary se!
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar

text: C110 family ka baap hai tu. Thank you for adopting Kevlin and me, lol. Campus mein profs se zyada tujhse seekha hu mai. Jab mujhe apne college ki bakchodi dikhani hoti hai mai tere baare mein batata hu. Bohot maze kiye hai apan ne aur karte rahenge, aur aage mere advice maangte hue calls expect karna,lol.
author: Vedant Sunil Kedar
